      "winemaking": "Whole-bunch pressing within 3 hours of picking. 10-18 hours settling. Spontaneous fermentation in traditional German oak casks (1200L Stückfass, 2400L Doppelstück) and stainless steel. Resting on lees, filtered in March, bottled a few months later.",
